Simply click DesktopPet.exe to run it.
Ps: Occasionally a bug may prevent the background window from becoming transparent; simply close and reopen the programme.
PPs: Once the background is successfully transparent, close the programme via the taskbar.

Left-clicking the character triggers a random action and expression;
Afterwards, it enters a standby animation loop;
The character can be dragged to move.

Character Art & Model: @ElenaMumu
Graphic Design: @维他米西
Animations sourced from Live2D Cubism Sample
Ps: As these were directly utilised, transitions between different actions may appear somewhat abrupt

